Title: Blooming Dreamseeds
Description: The Emerald Dream is about the harmony and balance of nature. For Amirdrassil to bloom, we need a rich variety of plants growing alongside the world tree. Plant seeds wherever you find fertile soil.
ObjectivesText: Plant dreamseeds in the Emerald Dream.
RewardText: Thank you! It's in these many small acts that allows the Emerald Dream to flourish, and thus nourish Amirdrassil.
